OL,4,CLionel Messi: Argentina forward banned
OL,5,Cfrom international football for three
OL,6,Cmonths
OL,7, Argentina captain Lionel Messi has been
OL,8, banned from international football for
OL,9, three months after claiming the Copa
OL,10, America was "corrupt".
OL,12,FBarcelona forward Messi, 32, was sent
OL,13,Foff in Argentina's 2-1 third-place
OL,14,Fplay-off win over Chile and later said
OL,15,Fthe "cup was fixed for Brazil".
OL,17,FHe has also been fined $50,000
OL,18,F(&pound;41,121) by Conmebol, the South
OL,19,FAmerican Football Confederation.
